{"tid":328994,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂- 超簡單 : 椰汁桂花糕","createTime":"2017-07-20T04:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T18:28:49.000Z","uid":30742,"like":41,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73c81b9537a0c686d1914fa3befbca3d6ae6250d","tid":328994,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XCicA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXCicA.jpg&h=6ce3dada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CXJhrZ62pYs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCXJhrZ62pYs&d=5%2Bt6gKX9MLuhq4I3ofa%2Fwcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=9bc058b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CXJhrZ62pYs</a><br />\n<br />\n之前因為係深水埗買左好多乾桂花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一口氣做左兩大樽桂花糖（其實唔應該整晒既&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n唔整都整左，都要諗計用左佢<br />\n杞子桂花糕整左太多次<br />\n咁岩之前返老家煮飯用左半罐椰漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就加埋椰汁糕一齊做，食落我覺得都夾既～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會話會比椰汁搶晒d味，反而我覺得仲好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且呢個真係好易做，個樣又ok，呢d整番公司請人食就最好<br />\n（我就拎左返去孝敬同事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=5%2Bt6gKX9MLuhq4I3ofa%2Fwcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=012350c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=5%2Bt6gKX9MLuhq4I3ofa%2Fwcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=82e4aabf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=5%2Bt6gKX9MLuhq4I3ofa%2Fwcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=745b1f89\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"13b33534f81b862b395b9025180df2553f58a2fa","tid":328994,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:33:46.000Z","msg":"老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf69ff5ca3dd0f99985c9ddf7be56f01349fb646","tid":328994,"uid":30742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783143cb1e972592b285c14eada48705f1e